# Tools

* ### PieDock
	PieDock is a task bar and application launcher in shape of a
	pie menu for
	[X Window System](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X_Window_System).

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in December 2010</span>$(loc ../PieDock src)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/PieDock)
	+ [Releases](https://github.com/markusfisch/PieDock/releases)
* ### cpprc
	Embed any data file into C++.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in December 2010</span>$(loc ../cpprc)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/cpprc)
* ### bbdock
	Displays transparent PNG icons in the
	[Blackbox](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blackbox),
	[Openbox](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Openbox) or
	[Fluxbox](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluxbox) slit.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in March 2011</span>$(loc ../bbdock src)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/bbdock)
* ### calc
	Line calculator in portable C.

	<p class="Stats"><span>Created in June 2013</span>$(loc ../calc)</p>

	+ [GitHub](https://github.com/markusfisch/calc)
